 increment per move from move 1.</p> <p>The games start at 15:00 EEST/12 noon UTC/14:00 CEST/05:00 PT.</p> <h2>Schedule</h2> <table><thead> <tr> <th align="left"><strong>Date</strong></th> <th align="left"><strong>Time</strong></th> <th align="left"><strong>Round</strong></th> </tr> </thead><tbody> <tr> <td align="left">5 May</td> <td align="left"></td> <td align="left">Opening Ceremony</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">6 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 1</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">7 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 2</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">8 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 3</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">9 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 4</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">10 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 5</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">11 May</td> <td align="left">--</td> <td align="left">Rest day</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">12 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 6</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">13 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 7</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">14 May</td> <td align="left">15:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 8</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">15 May</td> <td align="left">14:00 EEST</td> <td align="left">Round 9</td> </tr> <tr> <td align="left">16 May</td> <td align="left">18:30 EEST</td> <td align="left">Playoffs (if neccesary)</td> </tr> </tbody></table> <h2>Live Coverage</h2> <ul> <li>Live coverage of the event is available on the St. Louis Chess Club&#39;s <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/stlchessclub">Twitch</a> and <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@STLChessClub">Youtube</a> Channels.</li> </ul> </div><!-- SC_ON --> &#32; submitted by &#32; <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/ChessBotMod"> /u/ChessBotMod </a> <br/> <span><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/chess/comments/139d09o/superbet_ch